snippet.title: [MAME] Excite Bowling (c)2002 Epoch / SSD (preliminary, no controls)
snippet.description: realised I hadn't uploaded a video of this one.  This is some footage from Excite Bowling, it currently requires a few hacks to boot at all and has no controls (it dislikes our XaviX timer implementation and needs some input port bits to toggle)
